text: Krstel Petrevski (born 8 April 2001) is an Australian rules footballer who plays for Melbourne in the AFL Women's (AFLW). ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Living people Category:2001 births Category:Melbourne Football Club (AFLW) players Category:Australian rules footballers from Western Australia Category:Sportswomen from Western Australia Category:Indigenous Australian players of Australian rules football
